    public class NodeConnectorId
extends org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.ietf.params.xml.ns.yang.ietf.inet.types.rev100924.Uri
implements java.io.Serializable
    Identifier for a particular node-connector. For example: myprotocol: myprotocol:3 It is a good practice to always lead with a scoping identifier. In the example above the scoping was 'myprotocol'. In your app you could use 'myapp' etc.
